          "type": "faq_block",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "How long will it take to see results with whitening strips?",
            "faq_answer": "Results are often seen immediately after the first use! However, in an independent clinical study demonstrated that POOOF! is 2X more effective than the leading strips after 3 days and a 10-day in-vitro utilization, POOOF!® Whitening Strips showed 37% BETTER whitening than the leading whitening strips."
